title: Tin Foil Hat #62: The Black Eyed Children with Jessimae Peluso
description:
We're back!!!!! We're so excited to be back in the studio and deep into so crazy ass conspiracies with you all. This episode the boys welcome hilarious comedienne and host of "The Sharp Tongue Podcast"Jessimae Peluso. This episode we discuss.....
1) Strip bars in Vegas
2) The Art of Making Love
3) Horror Films
4) The Black Eye Children
5) Ghost
6) Aaron's love making ability
All of this and much much more. We definably go off the rails ,but man, was this a fun episode. Thank you for all of your support!
